{"tid":528941,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[原創歌曲] 貝多芬的情人","createTime":"2018-01-14T11:36:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T15:39:40.000Z","uid":98185,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"65419a424ab079e5445d0a7e40823af116c8fc22","tid":528941,"uid":98185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T11:36:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xR1eEd1lEm0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxR1eEd1lEm0&d=11Cbln4b%2BmRSnBXOWXylkv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=a5d2cfe1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xR1eEd1lEm0</a><br />\n<br />\n首歌表面上係講情人<br />\n其實係講。。。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&lt;貝多芬的情人&gt;<br />\n詞曲：Jason Ip<br />\n<br />\n琴聲跟我 又走到舊時<br />\n回味以前 那些趣事<br />\n旋律寫了贈一名女子<br />\n卻沒人在意 這一個女子<br />\n恐怕未叫愛麗絲<br />\n<br />\n又有幾人能遇見 童話故事<br />\n我其實也知&nbsp; 抱憾難避免<br />\n但痛苦其實可以 寫成趣事<br />\n將愁意寫作玩意<br />\n將頹志寫到勵志<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如今恐怕是 雙耳漸聾<br />\n誰在贊同 老天戲弄<br />\n琴聲安慰地 給來抱擁<br />\n那熱情熱烘 火燒到半空<br />\n可笑是耳朵未懂<br />\n<br />\n但兩手仍能伴送 旋律舞動<br />\n結局未揭盅 夢為何斷送<br />\n用我心陪伴一眾 音符跳動<br />\n雖然這雙耳漸凍<br />\n假如掏心聽便懂<br />\n<br />\n在這刻才明白了 誰的美妙<br />\n伴我同渡困擾 我便成就了<br />\n恨我竟如此可笑 春眠不曉<br />\n很傻的一隻候鳥<br />\n冬來方知暖重要"},{"pid":"6ac758739c3fb80d01be6acdeb4db98dba575abd","tid":528941,"uid":98185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T14:03:21.000Z","msg":"老漢推推"},{"pid":"6bde100d83689fb903e608add87266fd52b9fa75","tid":528941,"uid":98185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T15:18:01.000Z","msg":"萬彿朝宗!(我推~)"},{"pid":"da6974d0b0429df9ec196d12a81a1eda07562e83","tid":528941,"uid":98185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T15:12:56.000Z","msg":"有無ching 比比comment?"},{"pid":"728e80525d6a9ffe0194fb54be33a2a93b5b3fc1","tid":528941,"uid":98185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T10:50:09.000Z","msg":"last push ...."},{"pid":"c43f8d7e521349f35090d95f872e0e